Section: admin
Priority: optional
Maintainer: TrueNAS Team <support@truenas.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 13),
               cargo,
               rustc (>= 1.70),
               pkg-config,
               libc6-dev
Standards-Version: 4.6.0
Homepage: https://github.com/truenas/truenas_rust_nss
Vcs-Git: https://github.com/truenas/truenas_rust_nss.git
